snippet.title: Galaxy Arena Space Battles Cinematic 2
snippet.description:
Download game: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.cubyte.GalaxyArena.SpaceBattles

Galaxy Arena Space Battle is an addicting, space war strategy game. Join us in this space odyssey & be part of the guards of galaxy who are protecting the starcitizens in this huge intergalactic space war. Build your starship armada with dreadnoughts & other spaceships. Equip your armada with anti matter, engines & interstellar weapons to protect your space men & starcitizens in your frontier. Enjoy adjustable 3D view of the space war/ battle.
